title: My club has disappeared
body:
Hi my club that i am the LEADER of have disapeared for me. I asked my friend if he can see my name in the club ranks and he says i am still there.

If you have the same problem or have a solution please replay. :)

replies.body: As long as it's appropriate, what your club name and tag?  I'll take a look and try to get it resync'd for you.  Let me know!
Thanks!  I've resync'd your account to the club.  Relog and let me know if it looks okay now!
